title: Nordo in for PA! Heath/Micheletti/Birk
description: Eric Nordquist fills in for PA! MNUFC Head Coach Adrian Heath calls in, Pat Micheletti stops by in studio to talk about the new Wild GM, Cory Cove and Meatsauce play the NameGame, and Matt Birk calls in while on the road to talk about the latest news from the NFL!
